OL,5, A series of failures contributed to a  
OL,6, rail crash in Aberdeenshire which      
OL,7, claimed three lives, an investigation  
OL,8, has found.                             
OL,10,FA report said the train hit a landslide
OL,11,Fnear Stonehaven in August 2020 after   
OL,12,Fheavy rain in an area where a drainage 
OL,13,Fsystem had been incorrectly installed. 
OL,15,FInvestigators also highlighted problems
OL,16,Fwith operational procedures in dealing 
OL,17,Fwith the effects of severe weather.    
OL,19,FTrain drivers' union Aslef said it was 
OL,20,Fa "damning" report.                    
